Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸  我就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}正在現場進行全力營救 但還沒有發現任何生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  只有我活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}一旦發現生還者…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22\fad(200,500)}（心連心！）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然中途還以為會無法完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你們很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,借來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,投影機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  辛苦了  之後調整好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發表是在明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了哦  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你操縱投影機出錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的發表就付諸東流啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  最初的接待是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和須藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 在交班前我們就先自由活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看其它班級的節目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去看三年G班的偽娘咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,北村同學  你的興趣真特別…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  不是蠻有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們班級的節目是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,記得一小時內回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了  開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,味道一般般呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說得真直接呢  北村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 E班的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩真是喜歡那種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一人份  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出來的是36號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,36號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（神籤）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:05:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年會交到又高大又酷  既熱情又充滿魅力的戀人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西不用真相信吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出來的是52號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,52號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大凶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是宇宙人的後裔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天你會知道自己的身世之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像真相信了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是宇宙人還是其他什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會當你朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  接著輪到千川了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你來抽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「神籤」簡單說來就是測運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寫著好事的話  說不定就能打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大吉  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:06:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與你一直想見的人會有次命運的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川有什麼想見的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經是過去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到地雷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩做下問卷調查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初還不想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話沒想到你會認真到這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…你記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在避難所取材時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候須藤你這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做成成品讓其他人看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  相當…對於我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  虧我們特意提早回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  千川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  他說身體不舒服  去屋頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那大家四處逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…接下來的當班是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我和正久保
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  正久保和淺澤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時候怪婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像所看到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！這個時候不應該笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  你畫得太爛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與想見的人的命運的再會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  但這籤是巴迪抽的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪想見的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  就是在中心塔救了你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個不留地殺光他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是逮捕他還是去追他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯是巴迪的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又開朗  是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而我卻沒有看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是現在你也不願意相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當知道中杉是硫加的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不願相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以妨礙巴迪的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功很勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是心醉神迷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當時覺得失去中杉就像喪失自我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而忘乎所以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在一起就會覺得心情平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雙方什麼都不說也能心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也並不是愛這麼誇張的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  對於巴迪來說那塔魯也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人吻了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰吻了誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室…室戶先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了啊  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼青春的煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼室戶先生會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  虧我還作為報道研的前輩來看後輩的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也經常來這裡翹課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  但是翹太多課的話就會變得和我一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…大叔的話不願意聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有田紫苑  為什麼你會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還在你那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,車到手了  現在就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  在作戰地點集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我為什麼選擇這個星球作為逃亡地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想親眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加留下的爪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠被稱為究極抑制力的這個兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦卻將其封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不顧時刻緊張的同盟的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浸在虛偽的和平之下的愚民是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「聯邦需要硫加」這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這裡殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終究只是個阿留多的依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我像殺塔斯克一樣殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我了結你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點收拾掉那傢伙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙一定會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候就用這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校也老了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭弱小的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特爾已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,證據呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是他的擬態反應芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看下資料就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡爾塔克之狼的結局真是無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,委託已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你聯絡利比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  利比大人好像不太想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這和約定的不一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說好殺了卡特爾就能見到利比…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先違反約定的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒把硫加正確的資料傳達給我們就進行了實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並沒有根絕這個星球上的生物的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這也算是軍人的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能說是我們太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會向聯邦通報利比在這個星球上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能隨心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天他確實離開過一次房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但馬上就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,筋疲力盡地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在房間睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子狀況相當不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再把鎖弄壞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我單獨見他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我一個人進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？  那塔魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點！  那塔魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不能被你逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩三人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在殺光他們之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉羅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼要在自己家門前空等？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田小姐  我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡了多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一整天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令萊拉羅對你進行了當前必要的調整
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我調查了你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你已經知道我是依古西奧拉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會有不在聯邦政府管理範圍内的依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是調整失敗的缺陷品  正如廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道此事的伊茲達魯塔成員  把我從希馮的研究所裡偷了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生還是收留了那樣的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  老爸趁此機會脫離了組織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了撫養我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且沒有告訴過我任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我作為普通的阿留多人生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是在奧里奧特拉還是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天…各務在我眼前死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一個人  只有我活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠著依古西奧拉的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  為什麼現在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然是依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要使用那份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加把你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了活下去  沉睡在我體內的力量蘇醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至可以進行跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不該誕生出來的生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是古代帝國時代製造出來的兵器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們…不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但還不能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把他們全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標消失  進行了跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希馮  有通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今竟然來自首  你在想些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要退出這遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也厭倦四處躲藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我可不想被那個依古西奧拉殺掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  快帶我去奧里奧特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  沒有律師在場的話  關於事件的問題我是不會回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  居然還這麼得意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓你把中心塔的事情也一起說出來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克·米格亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那個啊  你還真是固執啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對這種陳年舊事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在盯著我性命的人對那次恐怖襲擊也摻了一腳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個失敗的依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到竟然真的是依古西奧拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯·吉利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等你很久了哦  那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特爾為什麼沒有出現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你殺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭弱小的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,內訌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接著就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢  我喜歡強大的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我好好享受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後  我們瞭解到愛存在著各種各樣的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有這種愛存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們人類面對任何困難…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說愛是不是太誇張了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  須藤意外地浪漫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  再還有十分鐘就開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也改不了原稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才開始啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了  早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  畢竟早宮要粉墨登場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神戶那邊還習慣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是個十分漂亮的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  千川沒在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙今天還沒有過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道又在做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮  稍微來一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在行李中發現了這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三個人拍了不少啊  大頭貼
